data.description: **Back on the market for a short time. Previous Buyers Financing Fell Through** Schedule your appointment to see this Beautiful Townhome in the Desirable Valleybrook Area of Blackwood! This 3 story stunning home has a newer AC unit, hot water heater, furnace with humidifier. Enter into the open living room and dining area with upgraded accents such as Pergo floors, crown molding. The kitchen has an open floor concept and will not disappoint with upgraded cabinets, granite counter-tops, stainless appliances, new sink and tile backsplash.  The second floor of the home which has Brazilian wood floors throughout is sure to please with a large master bedroom and bath along with plenty of deep closet space. The laundry room is conveniently located on the second floor along with another bedroom with wood flooring. The third floor also has Brazilian flooring with a very large bedroom with his and her walk-in closets and an extra storage area. Outside you can enjoy the covered front patio with exterior storage to sit with friends and family, entertain and have fun. The Homeowners Association provides a Maintenance free exterior and access to Valleybrook Swim Club, Tennis and Basketball. Come see this fantastic home in this great neighborhood!
